OL,3,CTen-storey tower block for Guernsey
OL,4,Ckey worker housing approved
OL,6,FA landmark new housing project for 57
OL,7,Fkey worker flats has been unanimously
OL,8,Fapproved in .
OL,10,FThe ten-storey tower block is expected
OL,11,Fto become the island's tallest
OL,12,Fbuilding and will be developed on the
OL,13,Fformer CI Tyres site at Domaines des
OL,14,FMoulins in La Charroterie.
OL,16,FThe land was and it is a major project
OL,17,F- the last time a building of such
OL,18,Fscale was given planning permission
OL,19,Fwas back in the 1960s.
