OL,4,Ckey worker housing approved
OL,6,FSome did share concerns about the
OL,7,Fheight of the apartments, a lack of
OL,8,Fparking and negative impacts on the
OL,9,Fenvironment but Deputy Victoria
OL,10,FOliver, President of Guernsey's
OL,11,FPlanning Authority, says this was
OL,12,Foutweighed by the need for homes.
OL,14,FShe explained: "Although reasonable
OL,15,Fconcerns were raised and considered,
OL,16,Fat a time when Guernsey has a
OL,17,Fparticular need for more key worker
OL,18,Faccommodation, on balance I'm pleased
OL,19,Fthat we could approve this
OL,20,Fdevelopment."
