OL,6,FA public footpath will be created
OL,7,Fthrough the site to the Area of
OL,8,FBiodiversity Importance on the land
OL,9,Fabove.
OL,11,FDeputy Peter Roffey, President of
OL,12,FGuernsey's Employment and Social
OL,13,FSecurity Committee, says more high-
OL,14,Frise buildings could help solve the
OL,15,Fisland's housing issues.
OL,17,FHe explained: "We need about a
OL,18,Fthousand units of affordable housing
OL,19,Fover the next few years if you include
OL,20,Fkey worker housing.
