OL,6,F"Obviously we are quite a developed
OL,7,Fisland already and that's going to
OL,8,Ftake up a lot more land so where it's
OL,9,Fappropriate, if we can build more
OL,10,Fintensively and build taller, we won't
OL,11,Fhave to take as much land as we would
OL,12,Fif we were spreading it over a much
OL,13,Fwider area."
OL,15,FGuernsey's National Trust also
OL,16,Fbelieves taller developments could
OL,17,Fhelp to protect the island's green
OL,18,Fspaces.
